rain; Charleston, S.C., 69 rain; Chattanooga 69 cloudy; Cincinnati
44 drizzle; Cleveland 45 drizzle; Detroit 39 cloudy; Hatteras 76
partly cloudy; Jacksonville 77 partly cloudy; Key West 82 partly
cloudy; Knoxville 68 cloudy; New York 52 cloudy; Philadelphia 65
partly cloudy; Pittsburgh 44 rain; Portland, Maine, 38 rain;
Richmond 68 foggy; Tampa 75 partly cloudy; Washington, D.C., 64
