<HEAD>Weather Editors</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   The national temperature tables with fixture numbers a9500,
a9504, and a9506 have been retransmitted to correct the low
temperatures for all cities.
   The error in the original tables was caused by an unexpected
format change at the National Weather Service.
   The tables were also sent as a9508, a9509, and a9510 to
accommodate computer systems that do not allow duplicate file names.
