<HEAD>Armenians Offer Aid to California Quake Victims</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-SF Quake, Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Tens of thousands of Armenians, whose homeland was
