Services appropriations bill, including language that would permit
federally funded abortions for victims of rape and incest.
   On this vote, a yes vote was a vote to pass the overall bill
while a no vote was a vote against it. There was no separate vote
on the abortion issue.
   Voting yes were 50 Democrats and 17 Republicans.
   Voting no were 5 Democrats and 26 Republicans.
   xxx denotes senators not voting.
